Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.52,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:150358,151525}{\fad(500,0)}Tōtō University Medical Center{NOTE:東都大学付属病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153904,154655}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156906,159868}No, no. It's impossible\Nfor my teacher to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.36,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:157783,158367}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:40.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:159868,160494}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:44.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160661,164247}I still have so many things\Nthat I have to learn from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.53,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:162995,163538}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164247,166541}Please, don't leave me, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167876,170671}How is she?\NHow is the operation going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171463,173924}It's been two hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.09,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:172130,173090}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173924,175133}Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175133,179846}That type of lifestyle…\NIt was just too much for her body to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180847,184559}Her heart was already bad, and then she had to\Ngo through the breakup of Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184559,186144}It sure was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186144,188438}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188438,191066}It's all because of that man\Nfrom Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:14.52,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:194027,194528}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200409,201284}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201284,203245}How was the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203245,205414}We did the best we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205414,207457}It's up to her will to live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213213,214131}Teach—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:47.89,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:222806,227894}Besides the time she spent\Nat school and on stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:53.90,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:227894,233900}…Maya spent all her time by Miss Tsukikage,\Nwaiting for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.78,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:235902,239781}{\fad(1000,0)}Tōtō University Medical Center
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.78,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:237237,239781}It has been four days since the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248999,252169}If you know of any relatives,\Nplease let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254337,258008}If she doesn't regain consciousness tonight,\Nthen she might be through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258008,260469}She's… about to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265724,267392}No!\NThat can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267392,268393}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268393,269561}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270479,272898}You told me you would train me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272898,275901}You told me you would teach me acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275901,276693}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276693,280447}Please, don't take my dream of being\N"The Crimson Goddess" away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282282,285243}"The Crimson… Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285243,287078}I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287078,290373}Not until I finish that project for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290373,292584}Oh, she's conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292584,293418}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304888,305931}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308058,309768}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309768,312813}The actresses who will play\N"The Crimson Goddess"…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312813,313647}…are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314680,316399}…and another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316399,317651}Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317651,319945}Teacher, who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319945,322072}You will know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322072,323865}Here, you need to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323865,325992}Don't excite her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325992,327536}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329204,331039}Maya, fight for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331039,335293}If you lose, the other person\Nwill take "The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337712,338671}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342259,345262}My face is burning,\Nso is my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349808,352518}I'm a candidate\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:57.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352518,357399}I'm always being corrected by her.\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357399,359734}My dream is about to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359734,363738}I don't know who this other person is,\Nbut I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:08.86,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:364948,368869}That day, "Wuthering Heights"\Nhad come to its last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369668,373272}I will die while you will become rich, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373957,374875}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374875,376209}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:25.21,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380797,385218}If you love her, watch her\Ntill the end, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385886,389973}Maya, why did you want me\Nto come and see your play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:36.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391308,396104}I'm hurt to see your love\Ntowards each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410327,415373}I'm hurt that you\Ndidn't even notice me hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.29,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:417834,420295}Backstage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418335,420295}Great job!\NYou guys did a wonderful job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420295,421963}Can I please get an autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421963,423715}Please sign this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423715,424758}Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425091,426509}Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426509,428678}Ms. Kitajima, any words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433725,436902}Did I lose to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436902,438396}No, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438396,439314}Ms. Kitajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439314,440231}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440815,443068}Here's a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443068,444653}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.61,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:444653,446613}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445362,447072}That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447072,450617}The man who always encourages\Nme with purple roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451785,453495}"Congratulations on the finale of your play."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453495,457523}"I'm glad to see that you\Nget better with each play."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457523,460961}"—Your number one fan,\Nwho is always looking at you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465590,466675}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466675,467842}Snow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469678,472013}– Watch out, you dumb ass!\N– Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485360,488071}For Kitajima Maya?\NNo, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488071,489864}B-But, I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489864,492575}I'm told not to let\Nany more fans in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492575,494160}Go away, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494160,495537}Oh, then, give her this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495537,496121}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496121,499416}Give this to Maya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499416,500875}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501835,503712}Shoot, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508258,511970}Maya, you have gone somewhere\Nwhere I can't reach you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:39.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513430,519785}If I only could love someone else.\NThis would have been easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519785,521395}So much easier…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.77,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:523313,526776}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523773,526776}Mr. Purple Rose,\Nplease watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:53.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527610,533074}I will be a much better actress, and will\Nplay "The Crimson Goddess" someday—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533074,535410}Excuse me, Ms. Kitajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535410,539164}Here, a high school boy\Nleft it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.12,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:539164,541124}Yū
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542250,543960}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543960,545587}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548131,549966}Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550425,552510}I don't want to end our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:17.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552510,557932}I will never be able to find\Na woman like you, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558516,561811}Ryo, you are just going\Nafter your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561811,565732}Catherine is gone with the stage\Nof "Wuthering Heights".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565732,568401}Please realize that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:35.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571863,575200}Sakurakōji, why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576910,578953}You didn't stay till the end\Non the first day either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:45.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580997,585085}Why didn't you congratulate me\Non the play's success?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593885,597597}Oh, Mr. President,\Nyou are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597597,600600}Kitajima Maya was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600600,602769}You have a great eye\Nfor choosing her, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602769,604687}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604687,605605}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605605,610985}Didn't you notice that the childhood Catherine\Nwasn't in sync with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610985,614072}Well, the critics have written the transition…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614072,617199}…from the childhood Catherine\Nto the adult one wasn't smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617199,620829}That's right.\NShe doesn't exactly know what acting is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620829,623748}Acting is about team work,\Nand not a one-man play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625792,627710}We won't be able to use her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627710,630171}That type of actress\Nmesses up the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:40.34,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:635176,640348}Miss Tsukikage's once life-threatening\Ncondition got better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:46.02,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:640348,646020}It seems as thought it lost to her passion\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess"…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:51.45,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:646020,651450}…and she spent most of her days\Nreading scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:58.15,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:651450,658158}The heart of Miss Tsukikage moved\Nfrom her condition to her next play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:05.20,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:660660,665206}In the meantime,\Nthey have joined Ikkakuju Theater…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:10.00,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:665206,670003}…who were visiting Tōkyō,\Nand planned for a joint play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.30,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:672338,676301}{\fad(500,0)}The Smile of Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673131,676885}This is our next script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676885,678094}The Smile of Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678887,681014}Now, I'll announce the casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685059,687353}Pio, a male swindler: Rei Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687353,688897}Huh, a swindler?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688897,693109}The rich daughter, Marisa,\Nalso, Hannah the maid…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689522,691065}{\an8}A man…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693109,694277}…Minazuki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694277,695653}A double role!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695653,698323}{\an8}The widow, Frederica: Sawatori Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.11,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:696905,701117}The roles were assigned one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698323,701117}{\an8}The Countess Isabella: Kasuga Taiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701117,703870}{\an8}Sir Goerge: Hosoka Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703870,706331}{\an8}The attorney, Prefew: Tabe Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706331,710543}{\an8}The relative, Gallison: Hotta Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710543,712920}{\an8}The landlady, Hinomiya Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707582,710001}I wonder what I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710001,712921}I'm sure you'll play the main role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712921,714547}Now, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714547,715465}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720261,723598}I will have you play a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723598,724807}A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724807,728978}Yes. A doll who just sits\Nin the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728978,731314}You won't have\Nany movements nor words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:16.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731314,736444}Why, why is she giving me\Nsuch a role?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:19.78,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:739781,739781}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:23.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:743493,743493}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:26.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:746454,746454}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753118,754295}I am Prefew, the attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754295,756673}I heard you called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756673,759926}Mr. Prefew, I wrote a will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759926,761594}I know I only have\Na little time left…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.76,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:761594,764764}"The Smile of Stone" is about\Na 12 year old, Marisa…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:48.10,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:764764,768101}…who is about to die after giving away\Na large portion of her property to a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:55.73,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:768101,775733}It is a tragic comedy involving a young widow,\Na countess, a swindler, and many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.32,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:775733,779320}Maya's role is the doll, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780655,783283}Oh, I want to move,\Nor to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783283,786911}This role is no fun,\Njust sitting around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:10.58,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:786911,790581}Miss Tsukikage started training\Nthe group despite her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791833,797213}Then, you will walk towards the doll\Nand push onto the doll's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797213,798089}Very lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799632,801509}Maya!\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801509,804012}You are a doll, not a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804012,807724}If you were a real doll, you would lean forward\Neven though it was a light touch on the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807724,809892}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810101,812562}Countess, go and push the doll again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813229,814939}And the doll falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814939,816024}Your elbow bent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816024,818568}A doll wouldn't try to cover her body, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818568,819777}Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821988,823364}Your hip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823364,826034}A doll wouldn't fall on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826034,828411}Why would you open your eyes when falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828411,830580}A doll doesn't have an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830580,833458}Your body is too soft.\NDo it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834417,835626}Straighten your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836878,839255}Your neck again.\NDo it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851267,852643}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852643,855271}This is not good for your body.\NWe should finish for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855271,858565}No!\NMaya, continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858565,859525}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873790,877502}I didn't think that the role of a doll\Nwould be this difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877502,881714}Well, in this situation,\NI'll become a doll, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881714,883633}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883633,884925}It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884925,886344}Let me hold her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886344,888304}No, you already held her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896896,898564}Become a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902068,904404}Miss, can we have our doll back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923714,926467}Mama, there's a crazy lady here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926467,928176}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971137,974015}Would a doll change\Nher facial expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974015,976100}I got the doll's pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976100,978603}But, I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978603,981022}I can't quite get the movement of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992450,998831}Well, but it's too bad that Miss Tsukikage\Ncan't come here and train us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998831,1001834}It's a critical time for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001834,1004420}I hope she'll get better by the day of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004420,1007924}That's why she needs to rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018935,1019936}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021729,1024815}Teacher, shouldn't you be back at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024815,1029403}I know, if your condition gets worse…\NRight, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030821,1033533}I'm okay.\NHere, let's get to training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033533,1034659}Maya, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046504,1047797}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048464,1051092}I thought you would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052260,1053886}Please go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053886,1056681}I wouldn't want you\Nto die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063145,1065439}– Maya.\N– Let her get up by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065439,1067817}Mr. Masumi, don't help her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069193,1071654}What's going on with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076951,1078661}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078661,1080663}No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080663,1082498}Don't.\NTake it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097388,1100308}What is this all about,\NMiss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100308,1104437}She's learning the difference between\Nthe body of a human and that of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104437,1109483}Humans have numerous joints,\Nbut dolls only have about five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109483,1114030}By putting bamboo all around her body,\Nshe can't use her human joints anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114030,1117950}This doll cast should teach her\Nthe movement of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117950,1119785}A doll cast…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119785,1121454}You didn't have to do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124290,1125958}Hurry! Take her to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125958,1127460}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129378,1132632}What the hell are you guys thinking?\NYou and her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132632,1137511}Mr. Masumi, has your father ever told you\Nthe story about my childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137511,1140973}A little.\NI know your parents died young…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140973,1143934}…and so you had to go\Nthrough many hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143934,1150733}I might have been dead, if Ozaki Ichiren\Ndidn't give me a reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150733,1152526}A reason to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152526,1154153}Acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154153,1159700}Because of acting,\NI am able to live, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159700,1163120}I want to give her\Nthe same reason to live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167541,1169126}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169126,1172421}Listen, don't do too much of anything\Njust because your wounds are not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172421,1173130}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173673,1175841}No bathing,\Nnor moving your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175841,1177635}Yes, I know.\NThanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177635,1180137}Does she really know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181304,1184433}I don't want to hear any more\Nabout what I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188062,1190189}Little girl,\Nlet me give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190189,1191273}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191273,1195069}I'd rather walk\Nthan have you give me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195069,1198531}You should accept it\Nwhen people offer you things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201200,1202743}You are so pushy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202743,1204912}I'm not trying to hurt you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204912,1207581}I just want to take you\Nhome safely, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207581,1209291}I'm not a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209291,1211961}I'm about to graduate\Nfrom junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212795,1215005}And which high school\Nare you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215005,1218843}I'm not. I'm going to practice acting\Nwhile working at a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218843,1222680}If you want to act, then you will need\Nat least a high school education.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222680,1225558}You should take school\Nmore seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226225,1228894}How do you think I can afford it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228894,1230563}I don't have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230563,1233149}Get away from Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233149,1236569}Metropolitan Entertainment\Nwill make you a great actress…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236569,1239363}…while supplying you with a scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239363,1241282}That was what you had planned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241282,1242658}I won't do it even if I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245494,1247620}Even if you were dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256380,1259175}Okay, take care of your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261761,1264221}Screw Metropolitan Entertainment!\NYou snob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268893,1272563}That reminded me about high school,\Nthought I was ready to give up…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.28,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1282323,1284283}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284533,1286619}Here, ramen and a potsticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286619,1288204}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294710,1296921}Haru, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296921,1300633}You're scaring the customers.\NCan't you do something about that cough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302051,1303427}Haru, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:54.27,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1311936,1314271}Principal's office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312353,1314772}What?\NI'm going to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314772,1319777}Some noble man said he'd take care\Nof everything, from tuition to board,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319777,1322446}And it's for the reputable Hitotsuboshi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322446,1324323}Hitotsuboshi High?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324323,1326784}They have great acting programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326784,1330454}But, who in the world\Ndid something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330454,1336252}Well, I didn't meet him,\Nbut he left something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339004,1341632}That's him!\NMr. Purple Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342591,1345135}"Please accept my good intentions."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345135,1352226}"I'm sure you will be able to learn acting\Nwhile enjoying your high school days."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:35.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352226,1355896}"I'm looking forward to seeing\Nyou grow as an actress."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357857,1361318}Mr. Purple Rose,\Nplease keep looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361318,1364154}I'll do it.\NI'll make it happen.
