Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:04.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1378669,1384799}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:10.88,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384799,1390889}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:22.89,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1390889,1402899}{\blur3}Something calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:35.03,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1402899,1415039}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:40.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1415039,1420919}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:47.04,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1420919,1427049}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:53.13,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1427049,1433139}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:59.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1433139,1439229}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:05.23,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1439229,1445239}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
